oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dubs of Unreleased Masters From MCA-Decca-ABC-Kapp - Tape 10
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The series of recordings feature Hank Thompson (musician) and Bob Wills and his Texas Playboys (musical group). The recordings were compiled dubs of unreleased masters from MCA Records, Decca Records, ABC Records, and Kapp Records. The recordings were compiled on an unidentified date. Tape is labeled as tape number ten.
